  <title>Game rules</title>

  <p>The aim of <app>Klotski</app> is to move the patterned block to a
   specific location. You must follow some rules while moving the blocks:</p>

  <section id="rules-block">
  <title>Rules to move a block</title>
    <list>
      <item><p>Click and drag the desired block to a location of your choice on
      the board.</p></item>
      <item><p>The green blocks and the boundary blocks cannot be moved.</p>
      </item>
      <item><p>A block cannot be moved over the green blocks. However, it is
      allowed to move a patterened block.</p></item>
      <item><p>You can take more than one step in a single move.</p></item>
    </list>
  </section>
